data.description: Four Bedrooms, Three Bathrooms, PLUS a Massive Three Car Garage AND swim spa! This beautiful home is nestled on a wooded lot in Harbor Place on Lake Tellico. An abundance of natural light fills the cathedral ceilings in the open-concept living room; flowing seamlessly into the kitchen and dining areas. The screened porch and sun porch are found out back with a private swim spa. Owner's suite boasts a brand new oversized, walk-in shower and double walk-in closets. Opposite the living area you'll find the den with gas fireplace and wood walls. The separate bedroom and bathroom in the den could be utilized as additional living quarters. At over 1,000 square feet, the three-car garage is deep enough for your boat plus a workshop area! 30amp outlet for camper or EV! See attachment for the list of multiple updates such as, windows, flooring, appliances, hvac, paint inside and out, and much more! *Home is in Monroe County, within the city limits of Vonore but has a Maryville address, so don't get confused by the location!*
